{"ProductId":"16","Title":"Avante<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> – Now Available with C-Power™ Technology","ShortDescription":"Aluminum and glass doors that make your garage a stunning focal point, providing natural light by day and a dramatic glow at night","Description":"","ThumbnailImage":null,"ShowcaseImage":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/tnahcpower01showcase.webp?sfvrsn=e1a1ed6c_1","CanonicalUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/avante","Overview":"<div class=\"d-flex mt-3 mt-lg-4\" data-section-id=\"Durable Construction\"><h3>Modern Style, Lasting Performance</h3></div><div class=\"d-flex mt-3 mt-lg-4\" data-section-id=\"Layer\"><h4>Built Tough</h4></div><p>The Avante&reg; features a strong, 2-1/8\" commercial-grade aluminum frame that stands up to daily use and weather, all while staying low-maintenance.</p><h4>Your Look, Your Way</h4><p>Mix and match from a variety of finishes &mdash; choose anodized, painted, or powder-coated frames, plus over 1,500 custom <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">Color Blast&reg;</a> shades. Fill your panels with tempered glass, acrylic, Polygal, or solid aluminum to match your style and privacy needs.</p><h4>Natural Light &amp; Insulation</h4><p>Let the sun in with clear panels or opt for frosted or tinted glass for privacy. Insulated glass panels are available for extra comfort and energy efficiency.</p><h4>Ready for A Storm</h4><p><a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/buyingguide/residential/windcode-residential-information\">WindCode&reg; door reinforcement</a> is available for homes in high wind areas.</p><h4>C-Power&trade; Technology</h4><p>Our <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/c-power-technology\">Click-to-Conceal&trade; panels</a> can instantly transition from transparent to opaque with the tap of a remote, providing on-demand visual privacy without sacrificing the door&rsquo;s architectural aesthetic.</p><h4>Environmental Assurance</h4><p>Clopay doors are compliant with environmental laws and regulations. Clopay doors do not contain HFCs. All Clopay doors are compliant with:</p><ul><li>California SB 1013</li><li>Washington HB 1112 &ndash; Hydrofluorocarbon Greenhouse Gas Emissions</li><li>Canadian regulations amending the ozone-depleting substances and halocarbon alternatives regulations</li><li>New Jersey A-5583/S-3919 &ndash; Greenhouse Gas Bill</li><li>Meets ASHRAE&reg; 90.1 Title 24 and IECC&reg; (International Energy Conservation Code) 2021 Section C406.9 Air Infiltration requirements.</li></ul>","Options":"","Construction":"<h3>Beauty and Strength Meets Modern Engineering</h3><p>The Avante&reg; is built with a virtually maintenance-free, commercial-grade aluminum frame that stands up to daily life and weather. Its 2-1/8\" thick construction includes Intellicore&reg; polyurethane-insulated rails and stiles (on Model AXU), giving you added strength, energy efficiency, and a quieter garage with an R-value of 3.8 when paired with insulated glass.</p><p>Every section of the door features tongue-and-groove joints and a section joint seal to help keep out air and water, so your garage stays more comfortable all year. For double-car models and wider doors, an integral reinforcing fin increases strength and durability.</p><p>Choose from a wide range of tempered glass, acrylic, Polygal, or solid aluminum panels to match your light and privacy needs. The rust-resistant frame and panels are easy to clean and built to last, with safety brackets included.</p><div class=\"options-container\"><div class=\"commerical-image-fixed-width-large\"><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-avanteax-1l-non-tg.webp?sfvrsn=621b921_1\" alt=\"Avante Construction\" sf-size=\"3022\" /><div>Made of 2-1/8&rdquo; durable commercial grade aluminum, making it virtually maintenance-free and long-lasting</div></div><div class=\"commerical-image-fixed-width-large\"><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-avanteaxu.webp?sfvrsn=b2614212_1\" alt=\"Avante Construction\" sf-size=\"2816\" /><div>Model AXU made of 2-1/8\" durable commercial grade aluminum with <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/intellicore\">Intellicore&reg;</a> polyurethane insulation with an R-value of 3.8 (with clear insulated glass)</div></div><div class=\"commerical-image-fixed-width-large\"><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/avante-ax-section-jointafbb6bf6-aae4-46fe-bfd2-9d85bb40efc2.webp?sfvrsn=7123d472_2\" alt=\"Section Joint\" sf-size=\"4196\" /><div>Integral section joint seal for further reduction of air and water infiltration</div></div><div class=\"commerical-image-fixed-width-large\"><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/avante-ax-frame-detail.webp?sfvrsn=c8ced87e_1\" alt=\"Avante Construction\" sf-size=\"1506\" /><div>Smooth flat frame edge design for a more contemporary look</div></div><div class=\"commerical-image-fixed-width-large\"><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/avante-ax-section-joint01.webp?sfvrsn=ba3d07b5_1\" alt=\"Section Joint\" sf-size=\"5242\" /><div>Reinforcing fin included on doors wider than 14&rsquo;. Standard doors 12&rsquo; and under do not use built-in reinforcing fin. Usage on widths 12&rsquo;2&rdquo; to 14&rsquo; depend upon glass weight. WindCode&reg; doors may vary.</div></div><div class=\"commerical-image-fixed-width-large\"><div><strong></strong>For doors equipped with our innovative and new <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/c-power-technology\">C-Power&trade; Technology</a>, all wiring is concealed within the door sections for a clean appearance and simple installation.</div></div></div><h2 class=\"h3\">Additional Features</h2><ul><li>Replaceable vinyl bottom weather seal in a rust-resistant aluminum retainer helps keep out air and water.</li><li>Integral section joint seal helps keep out air and water. </li><li>Built-in reinforcing fin provides increased strength and longevity. Included on doors wider than 14&rsquo;. Standard doors 12&rsquo; and under do not use a reinforcing fin. Usage on doors 12&rsquo;2&rdquo; to 14&rsquo; wide depends upon glass weight. <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/buyingguide/residential/windcode-residential-information\">WindCode&reg;</a> doors may vary.</li><li>A patented Safe-T-Bracket&reg; prevents serious injury that could occur if the bottom bracket were removed with the garage door closed and under tension</li><li>All <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/intellicore\">Intellicore&reg;</a> insulated doors come standard with 10-ball nylon rollers and heavy-duty 14-gauge steel hinges.</li></ul>","Models":"","FeaturesBenefits":"","SpringsHardware":"","GroupName":"","H1HeaderTitle":"Avante","DisplayIndex":9,"ImageGallery":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/image-gallery/avante","ColorDisclaimer":"<p>The Avante&reg; comes in a variety of sleek finishes to match any style. Choose from Clear Aluminum for a bright, modern look, or go with Standard White for a crisp, clean finish. If you want something richer, Bronze and Chocolate painted options add warmth and depth. For those who love darker tones, Black and Dark Bronze anodized finishes create a sophisticated contrast.</p><p>If you&rsquo;re after something unique, Clopay&rsquo;s custom <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">Color Blast&reg; program</a> lets you pick from over 1,500 colors, so you can match your home&rsquo;s style down to the last detail. While anodized finishes offer a beautiful metallic look, keep in mind there may be some color variation &mdash; for a more uniform bronze, the painted version is your best bet.</p><p><em>Due to the anodizing process, color variation may occur. The use of &ldquo;Bronze (Painted)&rdquo; is recommended\r\n        for a more consistent bronze finish color. Custom colors available.</em></p>","TopSectionDisclaimer":"","HardwareDisclaimer":"<p>The Avante&reg; keeps hardware simple and stylish. Each door comes with the option to add a sleek aluminum grip handle, designed for easy, comfortable use every time you open or close your garage. The handle&rsquo;s clean lines and sturdy construction blend well with the modern aesthetic of the door itself.</p>","DesignDisclaimer":"<p><em>*Only available on doors equipped with <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/c-power-technology\">C-Power&reg; technology</a>. Glass available in insulated tempered or laminated.</em></p><p><em>Satin etched is used in the AX/AXU models.</em><strong></strong></p>","RelatedProducts":[{"Title":"Modern Steel™","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/modern-steel-flush_fullview-window-black-garage-door-595.webp?sfvrsn=db7014e9_14","Id":"170","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/modern-steel-collection","DisplayIndex":7,"ShortDescription":"Subtle modern beauty, simple up-keep","AlternativeText":"Modern Steel"},{"Title":"Avante<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Sleek – Now Available with C-Power™ Technology","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/avante-az-595.webp?sfvrsn=70ef6b44_10","Id":"290","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/avantesleek","DisplayIndex":10,"ShortDescription":"Minimalist frames and slim horizontal windows for bright, unobstructed views","AlternativeText":"Avante Sleek"}],"ProductBrochures":[{"Title":"Avante Brochure","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/rsdr-avanteaxss-19.webp?sfvrsn=1d24e065_5","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-AVANTEAXSS-19.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":1},{"Title":"Products Available Through Independent Dealers","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-s